videos.description: The Giants' game ball goes to QB Eli Manning, who connected on a team-record 41 of 54 passes and led the game-winning touchdown drive in the final minute. The 49ers' game ball goes to Tramaine Brock, whose INT of Manning kept the 49ers in the game.
